Details:
Our main goal is to train the students in design field which can help them to establish themselves in the current competitive market.. We train employees to satisfyingly fulfill the requirement of their employer. People with many professions and occupations approach us for the solutions as they trust our quality & its deliverance manner. This is the reason, we are not just a training institute but we also deals in corporate trainings, services, colleges and project outsourcing too.
Mission to start this organization is to provide quality engineers and services to the specific industries. There are lots of job requirements in the engineering design field, but students are not able to establish themselves according to the industrial requirements due to the lack of industry specific knowledge. There is big gap between knowledge that a fresh engineer acquire and industrial requirements. We work as a bridge between these two people by grooming the fresh students according to the industrial requirements with the help of various training programs. We involve our students in various live projects, so that they can understand the current trend of market. We believe in quality deliverance. We do not believe in just imparting software knowledge to our students, but we prepare complete packages to get settled up and create a new workbench in the market. To motivate and to encourage our students we train them well for interviews, client dealing skills, personality development etc. Our vision is to provide quality training and designing services to our clients and establish ourselves as one of the premiere training and service providers in the field of Engineering.

Details: Avanti is an award winning social enterprise established by IIT alumni in 2010 to provide an affordable, high-quality education to disadvantaged students aspiring to study at Indias top colleges. At present, we have 80 full-time employees and 300 volunteers, and support over 1200 high-school students in 12 locations across India.Avantis work is helping create a dramatic shift in how students learn Math and Science. We implement a pedagogy called Peer Instruction that reduces teacher dependence and enables collaborative learning. Students consume lecture content in the form of recorded videos and reading material before attending class. In place of conventional lectures, classroom time is used to get students to work collaboratively on problem sets and clarify doubts by interacting with subject experts. Over the past 2 years, we have shown that our students outperform the most expensive after-school programs in the country at less than one-fourth the cost.Contact us for further details.

Details: EduCADD is an ISO 9001 : 2008 Certified CAD/CAM/CAE, Multimedia & Project Management Company headquarters in Bangalore. In existence for over 15 years we offer end to end solutions in CAD (Computer Aided Design), CAE (Computer Aided Engineering) and CAM (Computer Aided Manufacturing). To meet the growing demand in CAD/CAM/CAE industry and to meet our expansion plans we committed to Franchising model in 2004. Since then we have carefully and strategically spread our wings to over 40 locations in India and abroad. To touch lives by empowering individuals through training Exponential growth in the economy and new developments in CAD/CAM/CAE in the last decade has created a very competitive market place for job seekers and employers alike. We at EduCADD realized the wide skill gap between fresh engineers and the caliber of people required by industry. Most of our engineers are not ready for the industry even after scoring higher grades in UG program. Quality training delivery, better training techniques and tools and industry internships are the key to address the issue. Our Courses and its innovative training approach covers in-depth understanding to various industry verticals like Mechanical, Civil, Architectural, Electrical, Automotive, Aerospace, Shipbuilding, Heavy & General Engineering Industries and enables the students to have hands on experience. EduCADD has wide range of courses that are designed to meet the needs of businesses in different domains. Over a decade plus of experience enables us to provide excellent training solutions for students. We are proud of being acknowledged as one of the top training providers in the field of CAD/CAM/CAE/Multimedia/Project Planning & Management Courses within such short span of time.
